<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619403>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Oradarea dawa, new species, AM P64452: A, Pereopod 7 basis, showing scale patterns, scale bar = 30; B, Pereopod 7 basis, showing groups of scales with proximal insertion line and sockets where scales are missing, scale bar = 10. Iphimedia caledoniana, new species, AM P64453: C, Pereopod 7 basis, showing scale patterns, scale bar = 30; D, Pereopod 7 basis, close up showing groups of scales with proximal insertion line and sockets where scales are missing, scale bar = 10." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4619403/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

